      <title>月末动荡之际，美国主要短期利率飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/key-us-short-term-rate-surges-amid-month-end-turbulence-2024-10-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国关键隔夜融资利率周一大幅上涨，表明月底和第三季度末货币市场流动性收紧。]]></description>
